metadata.name: GM Coffee Token 1
metadata.description:
Starting the day every morning with a digital coffee and a warm GM makes life better. Although we may have never met in person, we feel a close bond through the morning greetings and virtual coffee drinking. 
This small gesture made the day a little better every time and gives the feeling that there is someone thinking about you. 
So the digital coffee and GM became a regular part of our daily routine and brings a smile to our lips every day.
